name: Pnut's Sister
description: CHLOE, $PNUT’s sister, has come to Solana to follow in her sister’s footsteps. CHLOE is running the Solana chain in the meme coin category. CHLOE is building a good and solid community which is very important in the meme sector! For the market, we will be integrating and collaborating with major key influencers, CEX listings, and utility development. Most meme categories can survive with a good community and partnerships, and CHLOE has 1000% potential to be the next one!
